{"tid":2101174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★以毒攻毒？電腦節2020｜電腦節如期8月中舉行","createTime":"2020-07-09T14:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T05:32:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6f0abdb53eb7771dea6f00b4a37ffac8c2f3f2","tid":2101174,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"本港新冠肺炎疫情反覆，由電腦商會主辦的香港電腦通訊節，將會如期於8月21日至24日舉行。今屆電腦節將以「科技&middot;連繫&middot;生活」為主題，並舉行首屆「健康與運動科技展覽」。<br />\n<br />\n電腦商會創會會長張耀成表示，除非政府要求停辦大型展覽，否則今屆電腦節將會如常舉行。商會亦表示，當局將於7月24日啟動會議展覽資助計劃，今屆電腦節將向展商及市民提供優惠回贈的措施，期望能幫助振興本港經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495896/%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AF%802020-%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AF%80%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F8%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B4%BE%E5%B9%B8%E9%81%8B%E5%8D%A1%E8%B0%B7%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F495896%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%25AF%25802020-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%25AF%2580%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259C%259F8%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258D%25A1%25E8%25B0%25B7%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25B2%25BB&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjqf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=dc2ba3b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/495896/%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AF%802020-%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%AF%80%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F8%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B4%BE%E5%B9%B8%E9%81%8B%E5%8D%A1%E8%B0%B7%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB</a>"},{"pid":"4c3c544347788d4217f7f92dd1c70d6409e3a7cf","tid":2101174,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\"